<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你还记得<delay20 />今天是烟花大会吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天晚上7点开始，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要记得来哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7点，<delay20 />万众期待的烟花大会就要开始了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />别忘了来玩哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎，<delay20 />烟花大会今晚7点开始，<delay20 />
你有空来玩吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很期待<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以和你一起欣赏烟花。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花大会<delay8 />马上就要开始了！<delay frames="40" />
好紧张啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你<delay20 />准备好了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />无论什么事，做好心理准备都是很重要的。<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这也是为了能更好地享受！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难得的烟花大会，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一起沉浸其中吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚天气这么好，真是太棒了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样的话，<delay8 />就能清楚地看到
天空中绽放的烟花了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚的天空<delay8 />被染成了各种颜色，<delay8 />
美得令人心醉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到就会觉得心口热热的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的烟花<delay8 />真的好棒啊～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看得<delay20 />太入迷，<delay8 />
以至于都忘了补妆。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">虽然烟花大会已经结束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但暂时就这样沉浸在大会的余韵中，
也是个不错的选择呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的烟花大会<delay20 />也都结束了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快乐的时光过后，
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总会让人觉得有些空虚呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过没关系，<delay frames="40" />
就让我们怀抱这些美好的记忆，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天继续努力生活吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00">今年的烟花大会都结束了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我已经玩得相当尽兴，并没有什么遗憾。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如此精彩，<delay8 />倒让我期待起明年了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />今年的烟花大会<delay8 />很开心呢！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等明年再次观看升空烟花的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会回想起今年的情景吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>